trans-unit.source: Visits each element of an expression tree from a given root expression.
If any element changes, the tree is rebuilt back to the root and the new root expression is returned; otherwise the original root expression is returned.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DefaultExpressionVisitor" /> class.
